## üîß Project Status

**PyEgen will continue to be maintained** for existing users, but new feature development will primarily focus on PyStataR. This ensures:
- ‚úÖ Bug fixes and compatibility updates for PyEgen
- ‚úÖ Stable API for existing codebases  
- üöÄ Enhanced features and new capabilities in PyStataR

